<h2 class="markdown-body">フローチャート記法</h2>
<p class="markdown-body"><a href="https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/" class="markdown-body">より詳細な使い方はこちら(外部リンクが開きます)</a></p>
<p class="markdown-body"><mark>以下は全て div タグの mermaid 内のみ適用されます。</mark></p>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph TD
    Start --> Stop
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph TD
    Start --> Stop
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph LR
    Start --> Stop
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph LR
    Start --> Stop
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph LR
    id1[(Database)]
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph LR
    id1[(Database)]
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph LR
   a --> b & c--> d
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph LR
   a --> b & c--> d
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph TB
    c1-->a2
    subgraph one
    a1-->a2
    end
    subgraph two
    b1-->b2
    end
    subgraph three
    c1-->c2
    end
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph TB
    c1-->a2
    subgraph one
    a1-->a2
    end
    subgraph two
    b1-->b2
    end
    subgraph three
    c1-->c2
    end
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">graph LR
    A[Hard edge] -->|Link text| B(Round edge)
    B --> C{Decision}
    C -->|One| D[Result one]
    C -->|Two| E[Result two]
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
graph LR
    A[Hard edge] -->|Link text| B(Round edge)
    B --> C{Decision}
    C -->|One| D[Result one]
    C -->|Two| E[Result two]
</div>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>例</strong></p>
<pre class="markdown-body"><code class="markdown-body">sequenceDiagram
    Alice->>Bob: Hello Bob, how are you?
    alt is sick
        Bob->>Alice: Not so good :(
    else is well
        Bob->>Alice: Feeling fresh like a daisy
    end
    opt Extra response
        Bob->>Alice: Thanks for asking
    end
</code></pre>
<p class="markdown-body"><strong>出力</strong></p>
<div class="mermaid">
sequenceDiagram
    Alice->>Bob: Hello Bob, how are you?
    alt is sick
        Bob->>Alice: Not so good :(
    else is well
        Bob->>Alice: Feeling fresh like a daisy
    end
    opt Extra response
        Bob->>Alice: Thanks for asking
    end
</div>
